{"TopicId":189681,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Add conditional action groups.","CreatedByName":"JhnGamz","CreatedById":201310,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-09T18:02:52Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"JhnGamz","CreatedById":201310,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-09T18:02:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdd action groups that only activate in certain occasions like liftoff or landing or in an orbit.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sidestrafe2462","CreatedById":165701,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-11T11:48:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOoh. This is good.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Thygrrr","CreatedById":170612,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-13T22:19:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFunny, I wanted to suggest the same. It would make uncontrolled descent \u0022easily\u0022 programmable.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor instance, on \u0022Loss of Signal\u0022, I\u0027d like certain antennas to unfold. (kind of a safe mode switch that I could set up)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOn \u0022Loss of Energy\u0022, certain solar panels or other parts.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOn \u0022Touchdown\u0022, certain decouplers etc.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-13T22:21:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou guys might like the Smart Parts mod.\u00A0 This is not a \u0022There\u0027s a mod for that\u0022 post.\u00A0 I\u0027m not negating the stock suggestion, merely letting you know this exists.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022129964\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed4570969827\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/151340-18x-smart-parts-continued/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:214px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"dnbattley","CreatedById":176526,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-14T03:32:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt would be lovely if the pressure sensor or temperature gauges could somehow be used in conjunction with a KAL action group in \u0022stock\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AVaughan","CreatedById":152784,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-14T07:56:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223704752\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022189681\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221573683712\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179753\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Geonovast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 hours ago, Geonovast said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou guys might like the Smart Parts mod.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr use Kerbalism, which also allows activating things when certain conditions occur.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(There is also KOS, but that is probably overkill).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Thygrrr","CreatedById":170612,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-18T00:04:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223704752\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022189681\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221573683712\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179753\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Geonovast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 11/13/2019 at 11: